---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Cafe & Bar East London | Speciality Coffee & Light Bites | The Hackney, Hackney Road E2" description="Dog-friendly cafe-bar inside a restored 1856 brewery on Hackney Road, East London. Speciality coffee, craft cocktails, natural wines. Two minutes from Cambridge Heath station. Walk-ins welcome.">
<!-- ==================== NAVIGATION ==================== -->
  

  <!-- ==================== SECTION 1: HERO ==================== -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg" role="img" aria-label="The Hackney cafe-bar interior with exposed brick and natural light"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="eyebrow">Cafe & Bar - Hackney Road, East London E2</div>
        <h1>Speciality Coffee In A Restored 1856 Brewery.</h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">A dog-friendly cafe with high ceilings, skylights and hanging greenery - two minutes from Cambridge Heath station.</p>
        <a href="#menu" class="btn btn-primary">See The Menu</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== SECTION 2: THE SPACE ==================== -->
  <section class="the-space fade-in">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="the-space-inner">
        <div class="the-space-text">
          <div class="section-label">The Space</div>
          <h2>A Proper Cafe-Bar In East London</h2>
          <p>We are at 503 Hackney Road, London E2 9ED, right between Bethnal Green and Cambridge Heath. The building is a former Victorian brewery with high ceilings, exposed brick, a skylit winter garden and a covered courtyard terrace.</p>
          <p>It is a nice place to sit with a laptop, meet someone for coffee, or come for drinks after work. Free wifi, plenty of plug sockets, and a good atmosphere all day.</p>
          <p>Dogs are welcome. You do not need to book. Just walk in.</p>
          <p class="history-note">Some of you might remember us as the Hackney Coffee Company. We started as a speciality coffee house, and good coffee is still at the heart of what we do. The space has grown since then, but the coffee has not changed.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="the-space-images">
          <div class="space-placeholder lazy-bg" data-bg="" data-bg-pos="center center" role="img" aria-label="The Hackney winter garden with natural light and greenery"></div>
          <div class="space-placeholder lazy-bg" data-bg="" data-bg-pos="center center" role="img" aria-label="The Hackney bar area with exposed brick"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== SECTION 3: WHAT WE SERVE ==================== -->
  <section class="serve fade-in" id="menu">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="serve-header">
        <div class="section-label">The Menu</div>
        <h2>What We Serve</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="serve-grid">
        <div class="serve-category">
          <h3>Coffee & Drinks</h3>
          <p>Speciality coffee made properly. Espresso, flat whites, long blacks, oat milk as standard. We also do teas, fresh juices and soft drinks.</p>
          <p>We also serve natural wines by the glass, beers on tap and soft drinks. For cocktails and evening dining, check out our <a href="/supper-club/" style="color:var(--fired-brick);text-decoration:underline;">Supper Club</a> nights.</p>
          <p class="serve-highlight">We make a good Negroni.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="serve-category">
          <h3>Food</h3>
          <p>Light bites through the day. Pastries in the morning, seasonal snacks and bar food as the day goes on.</p>
          <p>Nothing complicated, just well-made food to go with your drink.</p>
          <p>Our in-house kitchen is led by Chef Marco Mannoni. Seasonal menus, locally sourced ingredients, modern European cooking.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <a href="/private-events/" class="btn btn-outline-dark">Explore Events</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== SECTION 4: OPENING HOURS ==================== -->
  <section class="hours fade-in">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hours-inner">
        <div class="section-label" style="color:var(--dusty-coral);">Opening Hours</div>
        <h2>Opening Hours</h2>

        <div class="hours-table">
          <div class="hours-row"><span>Monday</span><span>Closed</span></div>
          <div class="hours-row"><span>Tuesday</span><span>8 am – 4 pm</span></div>
          <div class="hours-row"><span>Wednesday</span><span>8 am – 5 pm</span></div>
          <div class="hours-row"><span>Thursday</span><span>8 am – 5 pm</span></div>
          <div class="hours-row"><span>Friday</span><span>8 am – 5 pm</span></div>
          <div class="hours-row"><span>Saturday</span><span>9 am – 5 pm</span></div>
          <div class="hours-row"><span>Sunday</span><span>9 am – 4 pm</span></div>
        </div>

        <div class="hours-note">
          <p>On days when the venue is booked for a private event, the cafe-bar may close earlier than usual. Check Google Maps for today's live hours before heading over.</p>
        </div>

        <a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/RwT31Y6tmXPzyqGQ9" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline">Check Today's Hours on Google</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== SECTION 5: FIND US ==================== -->
  <section class="find-us fade-in">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="find-us-inner">
        <div class="find-us-details">
          <div class="section-label">Location</div>
          <h2>Find Us</h2>
          <div class="find-us-address">503 Hackney Road<br>London, E2 9ED</div>

          <ul class="transport-list">
            <li>Cambridge Heath Overground - 2 minute walk</li>
            <li>Bethnal Green Underground (Central line) - 8 minute walk</li>
            <li>Bus routes 106, 254 and D6 stop directly outside</li>
          </ul>

          <p class="parking-note">No customer parking on site, but Hackney Road has free parking from 7pm onwards.</p>

          <a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/RwT31Y6tmXPzyqGQ9" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary">Get Directions</a>
        </div>
        <div class="find-us-map">
          <span class="map-placeholder-text">Map - coming soon</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== SECTION 6: FAQs ==================== -->
  <section class="faqs fade-in">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="faqs-header">
        <div class="section-label">FAQs</div>
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            <span>Is The Hackney cafe-bar dog friendly?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">Yes. Dogs are welcome inside and on the terrace.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            <span>Do I need to book a table?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">No. The cafe-bar is walk-in only. Just turn up.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            <span>What are the opening hours?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">We're open Tuesday to Sunday (closed Mondays). Weekdays from 8am, weekends from 9am. Hours may change when the venue hosts a private event, so check Google Maps for today's live hours.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            <span>Is this the same place as Hackney Coffee Company?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">Yes. We started as the Hackney Coffee Company and rebranded to The Hackney. Same building, same coffee, same team.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            <span>Can I work from the cafe?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">Yes. We have free wifi, plug sockets, and plenty of space during the day. Lots of freelancers and remote workers use us as a regular spot.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            <span>Where exactly is The Hackney cafe-bar?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">503 Hackney Road, London E2 9ED. Two minutes walk from Cambridge Heath Overground, eight minutes from Bethnal Green Underground on the Central line.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== SECTION 7: CROSS-SELL ==================== -->
  <section class="cross-sell">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">More Than A Cafe</div>
      <h2>Planning Something Special?</h2>
      <p class="cross-sell-body">From intimate weddings to private parties, The Hackney hosts it all. Same building, same team, same attention to detail.</p>
      <div class="cross-sell-buttons">
        <a href="/weddings/" class="btn btn-primary">Explore Weddings</a>
        <a href="/private-events/" class="btn btn-outline">Explore Events</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== FOOTER ==================== -->
  

  <!-- ==================== JAVASCRIPT ==================== -->

<style is:global>
    /* ==================== PAGE-SPECIFIC STYLES ==================== */
    .hero {
      position: relative;
      height: 70vh;
      min-height: 500px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-bg {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: var(--brewery-dark);
    }

    .hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .hero-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin-inline: auto;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .hero .container { width: 100%; }

    .eyebrow {
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--dusty-coral);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .hero-sub {
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 20px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin-bottom: 36px;
      max-width: 560px;
      margin-inline: auto;
    }

    /* ==================== THE SPACE ==================== */
    .the-space {
      padding: 100px 0;
    }

    .the-space-inner {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 60px;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .the-space-text h2 {
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .the-space-text p {
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .the-space-text p:last-of-type {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .the-space-images {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .space-placeholder {
      aspect-ratio: 4/3;
      background: #3D2117;
    }

    .space-placeholder:nth-child(2) { background: #4A3228; }

    .history-note {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: 18px;
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--brewery-dark);
      opacity: 0.75;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }

    /* ==================== WHAT WE SERVE ==================== */
    .serve {
      padding: 100px 0;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(44,24,16,0.06);
    }

    .serve-header {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }

    .serve-header h2 {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .serve-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 60px;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }

    .serve-category h3 {
      font-size: 22px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      padding-bottom: 12px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--fired-brick);
    }

    .serve-category p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .serve-highlight {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: 18px;
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--brewery-dark);
      opacity: 0.8;
    }

    /* ==================== OPENING HOURS ==================== */
    .hours {
      padding: 80px 0;
      background: var(--brewery-dark);
    }

    .hours-inner {
      max-width: 700px;
    }

    .hours h2 {
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .hours p {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .hours-table {
      max-width: 360px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .hours-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 10px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .hours-row span:first-child {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .hours-note {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      padding: 24px 28px;
      border-left: 4px solid var(--fired-brick);
      margin-top: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .hours-note p {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .hours .btn-outline {
      margin-top: 8px;
    }

    /* ==================== FIND US ==================== */
    .find-us {
      padding: 100px 0;
    }

    .find-us-inner {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 60px;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .find-us-details h2 {
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .find-us-address {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .transport-list {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .transport-list li {
      font-size: 16px;
      padding-left: 20px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .transport-list li::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 9px;
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--fired-brick);
    }

    .parking-note {
      font-size: 15px;
      opacity: 0.7;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .find-us-map {
      aspect-ratio: 4/3;
      background: #3D2117;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .map-placeholder-text {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-size: 14px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    /* ==================== FAQs ==================== */
    .faqs {
      padding: 100px 0;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(44,24,16,0.06);
    }

    .faqs-header {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }

    .faqs-header h2 { margin-bottom: 16px; }

    .faq-list {
      max-width: 800px;
    }

    .faq-item {
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(44,24,16,0.1);
    }

    .faq-question {
      width: 100%;
      background: none;
      border: none;
      padding: 24px 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-align: left;
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      color: var(--brewery-dark);
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .faq-question:hover {
      color: var(--fired-brick);
    }

    .faq-icon {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 300;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
      font-family: var(--font-body);
    }

    .faq-item.open .faq-icon {
      transform: rotate(45deg);
    }

    .faq-answer {
      max-height: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: max-height 0.35s ease, padding 0.35s ease;
    }

    .faq-item.open .faq-answer {
      max-height: 300px;
    }

    .faq-answer-inner {
      padding: 0 0 24px;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.65;
      opacity: 0.8;
    }

    /* ==================== CROSS-SELL ==================== */
    .cross-sell {
      padding: 80px 0;
      background: var(--brewery-dark);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .cross-sell .section-label {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    }

    .cross-sell h2 {
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .cross-sell-body {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      font-size: 18px;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto 36px;
    }

    .cross-sell-buttons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 16px;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    /* ==================== SCROLL ANIMATIONS ==================== */
    .fade-in {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
      transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
    }

    .fade-in.visible {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    /* ==================== RESPONSIVE ==================== */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .the-space-inner {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 36px;
      }

      .serve-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 40px;
      }

      .find-us-inner {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 36px;
      }

      .cross-sell-buttons {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
      }

      body {
        padding-bottom: 52px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</Base>
